The following package should be installed before RainbruRPG is installed:

* Ogre3D 1.8
  + Needed.
  + homepage:
    http://www.ogre3d.org
  + download:
    http://www.ogre3d.org/download

* OIS 1.2.0
  + Needed
  + homepage:
    http::/sourceforge.net/projects/wgois/
  + download:
    http::/sourceforge.net/projects/wgois/files/

* Boost 1.55
  + Needed
  + Components: Program_options, Format

* CEGUI 0.7.6
  + Needed
  + homepage:
    http://cegui.org.uk
  + download
    http://sourceforge.net/projects/crayzedsgui/files/

* qt4-ruby
  + Optional : only used by the logreader application.
  + homepage: 
    http://rubyforge.org/projects/korundum/
  + download:
    http://rubyforge.org/projects/korundum/

* readline
  + Needed for server-ctl binary